### Old Payment Routes (DELETE)

#### [DELETE] [api/payment/instamojo/route.ts](file:///Users/rounakpaul/ncetbuddy-ed-tech-5/src/app/api/payment/instamojo/route.ts)
#### [DELETE] [api/payment/callback/route.ts](file:///Users/rounakpaul/ncetbuddy-ed-tech-5/src/app/api/payment/callback/route.ts)
#### [DELETE] [api/payment/webhook/route.ts](file:///Users/rounakpaul/ncetbuddy-ed-tech-5/src/app/api/payment/webhook/route.ts)

